title: Sex 01-09 (2013-Ongoing) (Digital)
description: Sex by Joe Casey, issues 01-09 collected. Published by Image Comics. Sex tells the story of a former superhero, sexually repressed and stuck in a new and unfamiliar role in the corporate world. Meanwhile, old enemies and allies (and those in-between) assemble around him in city filled with moral decay and depravity. Great stuff so far in the first year. All credit to the original uploaders and scanners. Enjoy and pleae seed, thanks! :-)
